ill be attacked by the merchants if they go in a shop.  All I know is that if I owned a shop in East Commons, and a bear walked in, I would not let it attack my paying customers!<P>--------------------<P>Host of the Newbie(r)Zone<BR>http://www.delphi.com/newbiezone/start <BR>    <BR>      Shokar Ke'Ravensali<BR>	Level 25 Paladin<BR>	Morrell-Thulle<BR>      Catyra Ke'Ravensmar<BR>	Level 22 Shaman<BR>	Morrell-Thulle
